# jlptcode Core

- Stack: Next.js 14 App Router, React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind, Material Tailwind
- Path alias: `@/*` → `src/*`
- Functional components + hooks only; keep components small and reusable
- Style with Tailwind; follow existing Material Tailwind usage
- Prefer existing patterns over new abstractions; minimal diffs
- Feature layout: `src/app/{feature}/`, `api/`, `store/`, `swr/`, `models/`, `components/Layout/`
- Client pages that use hooks/session/store: add `"use client"` at top
- UI strings: use `useTranslations()` + `src/i18n/messages/*.json` (ko, ja, en, zh, my) — no hard-coded user-facing copy
- Paid features: gate with `session?.paymentInfo?.isValid` and `PaidButton`
